snippet.title: Moose Boy - from the Nokia 5190 cellphone
snippet.description:
I've been hunting for this doodle for a few years now, since 2022. I had found a source online that said it existed on a chip inside the Nokia 5190, so I went ahead and bought one to take apart. I ended up opening 15 different parts on this phone looking for the chip, but I never found it.

Fast forward to now, and I saw a video from @Exciting__Electronics  where they opened up a really cool looking crystal oscillator. On the chip inside that oscillator was a doodle that looked very similar to Moose boy. This made me take a second look at the Nokia 5190, and I just so happened to have a bunch of 5190 scrap PCBs. I noticed that the oscillators on some were taller, so I opened one up.

As it turns out, Moose Boy is on this chip! So really it comes down to the luck of the draw if you are going to get an old enough Nokia 5190 that has this chip on it. I'm glad I can finally cross this one off my list :)

It features a flexible OLED display that wraps around the wrist, providing a comfortable fit and immersive visual experience. The SmartBand tracks vital signs Like heart rate, blood oxygen Levels, and body temperature in real-time, using advanced sensors and Al algorithms to provide personalized health insights and alerts.

Beyond health tracking, the VitalWear SmartBand integrates with your digital Life, offering seamless notifications, voice assistant support, and quick access to your schedule, reminders, and messages. It also includes a built-in mini projector that can display images or presentations on any flat surface, perfect for on-the-go professionals. Additionally, the SmartBand supports wireless charging and has a battery life of up to 10 days, making it a versatile and essential gadget for modern Life.

snippet.title: Introducing the "VitalWear SmartBand," a next-generation wearable gadget #ytshorts #trending #love
snippet.description:
Introducing the "VitalWear SmartBand," a next-generation wearable gadget that combines health monitoring, productivity tools, and entertainment features in a sleek, minimalist design. It features a flexible OLED display that wraps around the wrist, providing a comfortable fit and immersive visual experience. The SmartBand tracks vital signs Like heart rate, blood oxygen Levels, and body temperature in real-time, using advanced sensors and Al algorithms to provide personalized health insights and alerts.



Beyond health tracking, the VitalWear SmartBand integrates with your digital Life, offering seamless notifications, voice assistant support, and quick access to your schedule, reminders, and messages. It also includes a built-in mini projector that can display images or presentations on any flat surface, perfect for on-the-go professionals. Additionally, the SmartBand supports wireless charging and has a battery life of up to 10 days making it a versatile and essential gadget for modern Life
